| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-2894 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 743d1cf0-b6b4-5a2c-bcc7-8c032e56f86b"
